WEBVTT

01:09.569 --> 01:10.945
This was for Broc. I know.
You love him.

29:19.257 --> 29:21.176
You just can't destroy your
life for him anymore.

29:21.926 --> 29:24.012
-He's still with that woman.
-Not anymore.

29:24.304 --> 29:26.639
Plus, she's OK with it.

29:26.723 --> 29:27.891
That doesn't matter.

29:28.767 --> 29:32.395
You always think that, one day,
everything will fall into place.

29:40.111 --> 29:41.738
We'll be there for you.

29:42.238 --> 29:43.531
We'll take care of you.
